message.content: cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MED, cs.NEURON - This paper involves the use of deep learning for medical image segmentation, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI) research. Additionally, the focus on liver and tumor segmentation suggests a potential fit for the medical imaging (cs.MED) category. The use of neural networks also suggests a potential fit for the neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NEURON) category.
